text: This article is a list of events in the year 1993 in Senegal. ==Incumbents== * President: Abdou Diouf * Prime Minister: Mamadou Lamine Loum ==Events== *February 7: the delimitation treaty between Senegal and Cape Verde was signed ==Sports== *AS Douanes won the Senegal Premier League football championship ==References== Category:1990s in Senegal Category:Years of the 20th century in Senegal Senegal Senegal
